   - If `l1` is not empty, then `l1.length ≥ 1`, so `l1.length + l2.length ≥ 1 + 0 = 1 > 0`. Then `List.insertIdx (l1 ++ l2) 0 elt = elt :: (l1 ++ l2)`.

